The security architecture defines the set of properties which
structural properties
As a security architect, I analyze your system or infrastructure and identify
What assets in your infrastructure and applications need protecting? Against which threats? You care about the integrity of the data that goes into and comes out of your application, right? How do you guarantee it? Do you care about confidentiality? What technical measures and supporting processes can you put in place to do so? I give advice, but can also coach your developers and operational staff.
